     FFBCWP36AIF  E                    DISK
     FFBCWP36SO   E                    DISK
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      * SYSTEM TIME
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140WSDT
     I                                        1   60NOW
     I                                        7  140TODAY
      *
     I           SDS
     I                                        1   8 #PGM
     I                                      244 253 #WSID
     I                                      254 263 #USER
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      * MAIN ROUTINE
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     C                     TIME           WSDT
      *
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C                     READ FBCWP36A                 98
     C   98                LEAVE
     C                     Z-ADDTODAY     FSCRDT
     C                     Z-ADDNOW       FSCRTM
     C                     MOVEL#USER     FSCRUS
     C                     MOVEL#WSID     FSCRWS
     C                     MOVEL#PGM      FSCRPG
     C                     WRITEFBCW36S1
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
